name: MILLI
description: MILLI is a community coin on the Sei Network, notable for its rapid transaction capabilities. With the slogan, 'IN MILLISECONDS TO THE MOON - THE FASTEST COMMUNITY COIN ON THE FASTEST CHAIN,' MILLI emphasizes speed and collective participation. As of March 3rd, 2024, an ambitious goal has been set for MILLI to help propel the Sei Network to become the number #1 altcoin in the crypto space. Beyond its focus on speed, MILLI is committed to fostering an inclusive culture, welcoming a diverse range of participants to its community. Similar to some other projects in the crypto space, the team behind MILLI has chosen to remain anonymous, and, as of March 3rd, 2024, there is no comprehensive whitepaper available on its official website. However, this does not detract from its vision; MILLI is positioned as a mascot for the Sei Network community, intended to rally support and help grow the community. Itâ€™s a symbol of the community's shared aspirations and a token of participation in an ecosystem that values quick, efficient digital asset trading and inclusivity. MILLI has established partnerships with several NFT communities within the Sei Network, dedicating 35% of its total token supply to airdrops. This strategic move is aimed at enriching the Sei Ecosystem's growth. The airdrop was enthusiastically received by these key Sei Network NFT communities, signifying a collaborative effort to bolster the ecosystem's development.
